{"tid":1464070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"參考長榮罷工失敗事件","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:45:56.000Z","uid":110867,"like":117,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7f62d37eb409455ec14f50be352f799ef16c2d","tid":1464070,"uid":110867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1582047938532998/posts/2772625799475200?s=100001564176061&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1582047938532998%2Fposts%2F2772625799475200%3Fs%3D100001564176061%26sfns%3Dmo&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2mVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=b61a96f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1582047938532998/posts/2772625799475200?s=100001564176061&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n中華同長榮兩次既罷工最大分別就係，中華有民意，長榮無民意<br />\n中華爭取減少工時改善飛行安全，長榮爭取改善空姐待遇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有人話外國旅客對我地係無用，其實係錯。到今日仲以為我地癱瘓晒成個香港就可以成功？對中共黎講維穩先係第1，話之你佔晒全香港。<br />\n我地而加係要等侵侵出手先有勝算，如果破壞示威活動對外國既形象係無好處</span><br />\n<br />\n和你飛行動可以引起世界關注，可以繼續，但要搞清楚幾點！<br />\n<br />\n1.旅客不是我們敵人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6vMXmbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vMXmbk.png&h=d69a00ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pLdDX1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pLdDX1.png&h=e2750371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和你飛既原意係乜？提醒旅客遊港注意事項，希望佢地可以將黑警所作所為帶返去，引起國際關注，不是嗎？阻旅客做乜9，旅客係我地朋友唔係敵人！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.如果對遊客造成不便係必須，最起碼有預警<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yP0k3rV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyP0k3rV.png&h=cc94c8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VtB03rW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVtB03rW.png&h=7be7603b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以set deadline,如果政府無回應行動將升級，將成件事合理化左好多，亦對遊客不便減至最低<br />\n<br />\n3.不應以完全癱瘓為目標<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eM7Pcnb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeM7Pcnb.png&h=fe4cec7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyN7JtS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyN7JtS.png&h=bb623593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果有試過打風滯留機埸就知有幾慘，航班延遲1日對佢地既損失係好大，但delay就經常飛生，相信delay2-6個鐘對好多外國遊客係可以接受"},{"pid":"8af5a3fbb25cdc7c97ca3dc1824d0faba37676f9","tid":1464070,"uid":110867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:22:46.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967adbc80b6ce8969a18e3d06a377611fe4b13b6","tid":1464070,"uid":110867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c87e7fcedc3c2639b75af532be354c791e7c39","tid":1464070,"uid":110867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:24:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d4abb7dad7381398196d2da912e7964b191137","tid":1464070,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"8.13機場策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463429</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f247ab90f1574c70895ac9cb794054f4b612ba0","tid":1464070,"uid":110867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:25:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824a7920039a1a66c20ddd8f256ac05f10339d61","tid":1464070,"uid":110867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7606814a96cd3a6b9ed0d5e27e1f3c90e61115d7","tid":1464070,"uid":125194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:26:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c82395877