":0,"quote":{"pid":"219a54830fc2f58ed3f3cb8e525902dc2b8bbd40","tid":1464070,"uid":267454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee5c78b9d410080bc0592c0051e6ec8454e848f","tid":1464070,"uid":68471,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span><br />\n<br />\n（p牌狗用曬quota 出post，歡迎大家出post講）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"人多自然jam同主動jam真係有唔同<br />\n唔夠人做文宣啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:25:59.000Z","msg":"呢個係重點<br />\n我去接人機，吹？好難証明你係去非法集會定接機<br />\n機管局自己無啦啦停飛就上晒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:35:10.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n個feel係琴日係佢柒d，今日係我地柒d<br />\n不割，都請三思"},{"pid":"531cd5faf5bf15e231d00e92784a750173c49d79","tid":1464070,"uid":125898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f7f62d37eb409455ec14f50be352f799ef16c2d","tid":1464070,"uid":110867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1582047938532998/posts/2772625799475200?s=100001564176061&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1582047938532998%2Fposts%2F2772625799475200%3Fs%3D100001564176061%26sfns%3Dmo&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2mVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=b61a96f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1582047938532998/posts/2772625799475200?s=100001564176061&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n中華同長榮兩次既罷工最大分別就係，中華有民意，長榮無民意<br />\n中華爭取減少工時改善飛行安全，長榮爭取改善空姐待遇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有人話外國旅客對我地係無用，其實係錯。到今日仲以為我地癱瘓晒成個香港就可以成功？對中共黎講維穩先係第1，話之你佔晒全香港。<br />\n我地而加係要等侵侵出手先有勝算，如果破壞示威活動對外國既形象係無好處</span><br />\n<br />\n和你飛行動可以引起世界關注，可以繼續，但要搞清楚幾點！<br />\n<br />\n1.旅客不是我們敵人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6vMXmbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vMXmbk.png&h=d69a00ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pLdDX1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pLdDX1.png&h=e2750371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和你飛既原意係乜？提醒旅客遊港注意事項，希望佢地可以將黑警所作所為帶返去，引起國際關注，不是嗎？阻旅客做乜9，旅客係我地朋友唔係敵人！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.如果對遊客造成不便係必須，最起碼有預警<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yP0k3rV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyP0k3rV.png&h=cc94c8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VtB03rW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVtB03rW.png&h=7be7603b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以set deadline,如果政府無回應行動將升級，將成件事合理化左好多，亦對遊客不便減至最低<br />\n<br />\n3.不應以完全癱瘓為目標<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eM7Pcnb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeM7Pcnb.png&h=fe4cec7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyN7JtS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyN7JtS.png&h=bb623593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果有試過打風滯留機埸就知有幾慘，航班延遲1日對佢地既損失係好大，但delay就經常飛生，相信delay2-6個鐘對好多外國遊客係可以接受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66556938290cf1737bbcc2fec9802c56e93ed85b","tid":1464070,"uid":19581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"Delay咁耐 外國人人生路不熟 真係會好無助"},{"pid":"6170fad33ea218595aff599e3ecca5f54e142489","tid":1464070,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}